#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/for-maintainability/rust-specific/functions-and-methods.md:80
msgid "Introduce explaining variables (`explain-variables`)"
msgstr ""

#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/for-maintainability/rust-specific/functions-and-methods.md:82
msgid ""
"Break down complex expressions by assigning intermediate results to well-"
"named variables. An explaining variable turns an opaque expression into self-"
"documenting code:"
msgstr ""

